OL,3,CArmy officers deny charges after
OL,4,Csoldier took own life after sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FTwo senior Army officers have denied
OL,8,Fcharges brought following the death of
OL,9,Fyoung soldier who took her own life
OL,10,Fafter she was sexually assaulted by a
OL,11,Fsuperior.
OL,13,FColonel Samantha Shepherd and Major
OL,14,FJames Hook appeared at the Military
OL,15,FCourt Centre at Catterick Garrison, in
OL,16,FNorth Yorkshire, by video-link on
OL,17,FWednesday, where they both denied
OL,18,F"conduct prejudicial to good order and
OL,19,Fservice discipline".
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@SO]
