OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773349947
OL,3,CArmy officers deny charges after
OL,4,Csoldier took own life after sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FThe allegations they face relate to
OL,8,Fhow they handled information before
OL,9,FJaysley Beck was found dead in her
OL,10,Fbarracks in Larkhill Camp, Wiltshire,
OL,11,Fin 2021.
OL,13,FFormer senior non-commissioned officer
OL,14,FMichael Webber, 43, was jailed for six
OL,15,Fmonths by a military court last year
OL,16,Fafter pleading guilty to sexually
OL,17,Fassaulting Gunner Beck five months
OL,18,Fbefore her death.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
