FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773349947
OL,3,CArmy officers deny charges after
OL,4,Csoldier took own life after sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FAn inquest into the 19-year-old's
OL,8,Fdeath found the incident and the
OL,9,FArmy's failure to take appropriate
OL,10,Faction "more than minimally"
OL,11,Fcontributed to her death.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, Shepherd pleaded not
OL,14,Fguilty to two charges of conduct
OL,15,Fprejudicial to good order and service
OL,16,Fdiscipline.
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@\O]
