CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773349947
OL,3,CArmy officers deny charges after
OL,4,Csoldier took own life after sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FThe first alleges that "on July 13,
OL,8,F2021, and thereafter, you did not
OL,9,Freport the commission of an alleged
OL,10,Fsexual assault to the service police
OL,11,Fin respect of a suspect within the
OL,12,Fregiment of which you were regimental
OL,13,Fcolonel".
OL,15,FThe second alleges that "on a date in
OL,16,FJuly 2021, you misreported what you
OL,17,Fhad been told by Jaysley Beck" to
OL,18,Fanother person.
OL,20,FHook pleaded not guilty to one charge
OL,21,Fof the same offence.
OL,26,@oD@XOUuD@HO]wD@YOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
