FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773349947
OL,3,CArmy officers deny charges after
OL,4,Csoldier took own life after sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FThis alleges that "on July 13, 2021
OL,8,Fyou did not treat information passed
OL,9,Fto yourself by Jaysley Beck in a
OL,10,Fmanner consistent with its
OL,11,Fseriousness".
OL,13,FJudge Adjutant General Alan Large told
OL,14,Fthe defendants they will go on trial
OL,15,Fon 14 September, but it has not yet
OL,16,Fbeen decided whether the five-day
OL,17,Fhearing will be at Catterick or at
OL,18,FBulford Camp in Wiltshire.
OL,20,FA further case management hearing will
OL,21,Fbe held on 23 June
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@LO]
