OL,3,CArmy officers deny charges after
OL,4,Csoldier took own life after sexual
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FA number of Gunner Beck's family were
OL,8,Fon the link listening to the 20-minute
OL,9,Fhearing.
OL,11,FThe judge was told Hook is serving
OL,12,Fwith 29 Commando Regiment Royal
OL,13,FArtillery and Shepherd, who appeared
OL,14,Ffrom the United States, is serving
OL,15,Fwith the British Defence Staff in the
OL,16,Fcountry.
